cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on learning visuomotor skills for robots and evaluating the method on physical arms.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper introduces an end-to-end method for learning goal-parameterized neural network policies.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper involves training a policy using deep learning techniques.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as the paper uses visual data to infer the specific target for the robot.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper involves controlling physical systems (robot arms) to achieve a specific goal.
